originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.Id AS PostId,
    p.Title,
    p.CreationDate,
    p.Score,
    p.ViewCount,
    u.DisplayName AS OwnerDisplayName,
    u.Reputation AS OwnerReputation,
    p.AnswerCount,
    COALESCE(c.CommentCount, 0) AS CommentCount,
    COALESCE(pl.LinksCount, 0) AS LinksCount,
    COALESCE(ph.HistoryCount, 0) AS HistoryCount
FROM 
    Posts p
JOIN 
    Users u ON p.OwnerUserId = u.Id
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT PostId, COUNT(*) AS CommentCount FROM Comments GROUP BY PostId) c ON p.Id = c.PostId
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT PostId, COUNT(*) AS LinksCount FROM PostLinks GROUP BY PostId) pl ON p.Id = pl.PostId
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT PostId, COUNT(*) AS HistoryCount FROM PostHistory GROUP BY PostId) ph ON p.Id = ph.PostId
WHERE 
    p.CreationDate >= cast('2024-10-01' as date) - INTERVAL '1' YEAR 
ORDER BY 
    p.Score DESC, 
    p.CreationDate DESC
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("Posts"."Id", "Posts"."Id") AS "POSTID", "Posts"."Title" AS "TITLE", "Posts"."CreationDate" AS "CREATIONDATE", "Posts"."Score" AS "SCORE", "Posts"."ViewCount" AS "VIEWCOUNT", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "OWNERDISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "OWNERREPUTATION", "Posts"."AnswerCount" AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t2"."COMMENTCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t2"."COMMENTCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "COMMENTCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."LINKSCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."LINKSCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "LINKSCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t5"."HISTORYCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t5"."HISTORYCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "HISTORYCOUNT"
FROM "Posts"
INNER JOIN "Users" ON "Posts"."OwnerUserId" = "Users"."Id"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", COUNT(*) AS "COMMENTCOUNT"
FROM "Comments"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t2" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t2"."POSTID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", COUNT(*) AS "LINKSCOUNT"
FROM "PostLinks"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t4" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t4"."POSTID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "POSTID", COUNT(*) AS "HISTORYCOUNT"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "POSTID") AS "t5" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t5"."POSTID"
WHERE "Posts"."CreationDate" >= CAST((CAST('2024-10-01' AS DATE) - INTERVAL '1' YEAR) AS TIMESTAMP)
ORDER BY "Posts"."Score" DESC NULLS FIRST, "Posts"."CreationDate" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100
